- services will share the common business logic to the all the controllers that are available in angular application.

- we have two types of services.
    1.Custom Services
    2.Predefined Services

1.Custom Service.
    - The Services Developed by developer based on application requirement called as Custom Services.

    - we can create the custom services in five ways.
            1.provider()
            2.factory()
            3.value()
            4.constant()
            5.service()



2.Predefined Services.
   - The Services Provided by the Framework called as Predefined Services.

   $http

        - used to connect to servers via http protocol.






